ny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="哈尔西和莱尼·克拉维茨。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage 和 Marc Atkins/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Halsey-and-Lenny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Halsey-and-Lenny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Halsey-and-Lenny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Halsey-and-Lenny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Halsey-and-Lenny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Halsey-and-Lenny-Kravitz.-Credit_-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Marc-Atkins_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Halsey">Halsey</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lenny-kravitz">Lenny Kravitz</a>已被宣布为即将举行的 2024 年 MTV 音乐录影带大奖的表演者。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lSNvxjY_aBk"><b>哈尔西谈一年的“如果我不能拥有爱，我想要权力”，报道凯特·布什和《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》</b></a></li></ul><p>该仪式原定于 9 月 10 日在纽约举行 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-postponed-due-to-trump-vs-harris-debate-3783163">，但最近改期至 9 月 11 日，</a>以避免与电视转播的总统辩论发生冲突，这将是候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯</a>首次面对面。</p><p>现在，宣布哈尔西和克拉维茨将加入先前宣布的表演者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">萨布丽娜·卡彭特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">卡米拉·卡贝洛、</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glorilla">格洛里拉</a>和劳夫·亚历杭德罗的行列，他们都将在今年获奖。</p><p>昨天（8 月 21 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benson-boone">，Benson Boone</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">Blackpink</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">Lisa</a>也被宣布为表演者。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-84pt5xx6G/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.34